sequenceDiagram
    participant O as Orchestrator
    participant D as Diagram
    participant T1 as Task Agent 1
    participant T2 as Task Agent 2
    participant T3 as Task Agent 3

    Note over O: Parallel dispatch starts
    O->>D: Update all to executing
    O->>T1: Spawn task 1
    O->>T2: Spawn task 2
    O->>T3: Spawn task 3

    Note over O: Waiting for ALL...
    T1-->>O: Complete
    Note over D: T1 done but diagram unchanged
    T2-->>O: Complete
    Note over D: T2 done but diagram unchanged
    T3-->>O: Complete
    Note over D: T3 done but diagram unchanged

    Note over O: ALL tasks returned
    O->>D: Update all to completed

    rect rgb(255, 200, 200)
        Note over D: Gap: No updates while<br/>individual tasks complete
    end